# 🤖 AI Test Automation Agent Framework

An AI-powered UI Test Automation Framework built using **LangGraph**, **LangChain**, **Playwright**, and **Ollama**. This framework enables a Large Language Model (LLM) to understand natural language instructions, invoke browser automation tools, execute end-to-end UI actions, capture screenshots, generate execution reports, and provide failure analysis for debugging.

---

# 🎯 Project Objective

Traditional automation frameworks require manually written test scripts.

This framework introduces an AI Agent capable of:

* Understanding test steps written in natural language.
* Deciding which automation tool to invoke.
* Executing browser actions autonomously.
* Capturing execution evidence.
* Generating HTML reports.
* Assisting in failure analysis.

The goal is to reduce scripting effort while making UI automation more intelligent, maintainable, and scalable.

---

# 🚀 Technology Stack

| Component            | Technology                |
| -------------------- | ------------------------- |
| Programming Language | Python 3.x                |
| AI Framework         | LangGraph                 |
| LLM Integration      | LangChain                 |
| Browser Automation   | Playwright                |
| LLM                  | Ollama (Qwen Model)       |
| Reporting            | Custom HTML Report        |
| Screenshots          | Playwright Screenshot API |
| Async Programming    | asyncio                   |

---

# 🧠 LLM Model

Current Model:

```
qwen2.5:0.5b
```

Recommended Models:

* qwen3:4b
* qwen2.5:3b
* llama3.1:8b

Larger models generally provide more reliable multi-step reasoning and tool-calling.

---

# 🏗 Framework Architecture

```
                   User Prompt
                        │
                        ▼
               LangGraph AI Agent
                        │
                LangChain Tool Calling
                        │
      ┌─────────────────┼────────────────┐
      │                 │                │
      ▼                 ▼                ▼
 Browser Manager     Playwright      Report Manager
      │                 │                │
      ▼                 ▼                ▼
 Browser Actions   Screenshots      HTML Report
                        │
                        ▼
               Failure Analysis Agent
```

